{"tid":1831572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴我屌你老母","createTime":"2020-01-20T13:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T10:12:38.000Z","uid":316700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b81a3a1856d8e184bde3232fc0190cfbecef78a","tid":1831572,"uid":316700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"我真係屌你個老母閪<br />\n平時59X就識開5、6分鐘甚至4分鐘一班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過就轉車站返屯門個服務就閪到震<br />\n可以百零人排隊 三四班車上唔到<br />\n就算我成日旺角揀位直車返去都睇唔過眼<br />\n而且一唔中意就踢落9-1x分鐘 <br />\n最撚嬲係咩 我屌你個閪<br />\n就係60X繼續準時開同埋佢哋轉車站多車又少人排<br />\n我屌你老母 踢263 61X直上公路啦<br />\n唔係市中心嘅人憑咩痴餐呀 慳返啲時間用嚟加班好過啦<br />\n屌你老母朝早見到263 未到轉車站已經坐滿<br />\n跟住有人仲要等下一班<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J3rfH1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3rfH1e.png&h=5d226e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有 我重你老母視咩九巴<br />\n淨係識恰鳩屯門碼頭 <br />\n屌你老母閪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zmoqkRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmoqkRy.png&h=fa720dbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdbcef5a9494ab7045f0c80ed2929d7061e11a60","tid":1831572,"uid":316700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"一齊轉車啦你班既得利益者<br />\n仲有呀 就嚟過年<br />\n又係時候體驗下上唔到車嘅感覺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44afdb046a5ad6ea6882a1bd9f5cf51c06d315cb","tid":1831572,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"老狗：唔鐘意咪去坐962X囉"},{"pid":"6a30b0fcf04536fd17c85024b4d25eca0dd5ac32","tid":1831572,"uid":258631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"咁你寧願排耐啲 定條隊去晒搭黨鐵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d736a6ebb7c97990143906dac1e08af103f2c2","tid":1831572,"uid":316